title: NASA and The Third Reich: A Partnership For Alien Communication?
description:
My special guest tonight is author and researcher Mary Joyce who is the writer of the blog Sky Ships Over Cashiers. She discusses the details of a former NASA employee who claimed to know and witness incredible events that occurred during his employment before he died.
